rbohydrates":"35 g","calories":"1497 kJ \/ 357 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl, ThermoServer, large serving bowl","hintsAndTricks":["Substitute frozen green peas with canned green peas, drained. Add at the end of step 2 into the ThermoServer or serving bowl with the pasta and extra virgin olive oil.","Garnish with chopped parsley, to taste.","Choose pasta with a 10 minute cooking time.","Trout or salmon can also be substituted with swordfish fillets. Depending on the quality and type of fish, steaming time in step 1 can be adjusted to your preference.","If you prefer bigger pieces of fish, don’t add fish into the mixing bowl in step 4. Instead, cut fish into pieces and gently combine it into the salad with the spatula.","If you prefer a stronger garlic flavour, rather than removing the garlic clove, chop <strong>5 sec\/speed<strong> <\/strong>6<\/strong> in step 3 before sautéing."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","6 portions"]}